{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"element.dispatchEvent","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Metody</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>addEventListener()</code></a></li><li><em><code>dispatchEvent()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/removeEventListener\"><code>removeEventListener()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Wywołuje zdarzenie w bieżącym elemencie.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><em>bool</em> = <em>element</em>.dispatchEvent(<em>event</em>)\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>event</code> to <a href=\"pl/DOM/event\">obiekt zdarzenia</a>, które ma zostać wywołane.</li>\n <li>Jeśli któraś z funkcji obsługujących to zdarzenie wywoła <a href=\"pl/DOM/event.preventDefault\">preventDefault</a>, zwracana wartość to <code>false</code>. W przeciwnym przypadku zwracane jest <code>true</code>.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Jak pokazuje powyższy przykład, <code>dispatchEvent</code> to ostatni krok w procesie utwórz-zainicjuj-wywołaj, którego używa się by ręcznie wywołać zdarzenia w modelu zdarzeń implementacji.</p>\n\n<p>Zdarzenie może zostać utworzone przy użyciu metody <a href=\"pl/DOM/document.createEvent\">document.createEvent</a> i zainicjowane za pomocą <a href=\"pl/DOM/event.initEvent\">initEvent</a> lub innej, bardziej wyspecjalizowanej metody, jak <a href=\"pl/DOM/event.initMouseEvent\">initMouseEvent</a> albo <a href=\"pl/DOM/event.initUIEvent\">initUIEvent</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Zobacz też dokumentację <a href=\"pl/DOM/event\">obiektu event</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Events/events.html#Events-EventTarget-dispatchEvent\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Events: dispatchEvent</a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Wywołuje zdarzenie w bieżącym elemencie.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"element.dispatchEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.dispatchEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"EventTarget.dispatchEvent()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/eventtarget/dispatchevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/eventtarget/dispatchevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/dispatchEvent","title":"element.dispatchEvent"}],"pageTitle":"element.dispatchEvent - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}